In the issue navigator, there is no way to search for comments that have been added or edited within a specified timeframe. When searching for updates in a large database, it would be extremely useful to specify comment updates, rather than any change made. In addition, having all the comments display on one page, rather than a list of bugs for the added comments would be extremely useful for reports.

