The single group by report function only pulls bugs from a filter and sorts them by the specified field. It would be a useful addition to have a "include comments" checkbox on the screen that allows you to select what field to sort by. This feature could include all new or edited comments within a specified timeframe in a formatted view that could appear below the group of bugs within the Single Group by Report. 

These reports are extremely useful, and having any new comments available at a whim would greatly improve the usefulness of the Single Group by Report feature.

